ón global","guid":"YfeTIJ2N1oDIDolZw6VZ8A","children":[{"id":"335","parent":"334","text":"Enfermedad de graves","guid":"Xo343q4EiseVhwzftT3JuQ","children":[]},{"id":"336","parent":"334","text":"Tumores productores de TSH","guid":"4bO_fb5yLXNqWhsora_v0w","children":[]},{"id":"337","parent":"334","text":"Tumores productores de hCG","guid":"NarzfOyRQLkbs_bqr5ZV0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"338","parent":"333","text":">Captación localizada","guid":"e6HsaKqqRon56MHgUfIMYw","children":[{"id":"339","parent":"338","text":"BMNT","guid":"BnEWVc-UF4vPQq1CuerpXQ","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"338","text":"Adenoma tóxico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"341","parent":"332","text":"<Captación\\NLiberación ya formado (inflamación) o exógeno","guid":"F5ZsCbGB62LX4_mJ23I6uQ","children":[{"id":"342","parent":"341","text":"Tiroiditis","guid":"M2CbyTdNAiDuPHIqNHH4ng","children":[]},{"id":"343","parent":"341","text":"Fenómeno de\\NJob-Basedow","guid":"b9-0kgWxgF3zDYLqrUw4WA","children":[{"id":"344","parent":"343","text":"Yodo en nódulos\\Nfuncionamiento autónomo","guid":"Hl1MtSz0G4-Cn_xIANQ0Hw","children":[]}]},{"id":"345","parent":"341","text":"Tirotoxicosis fáctica","guid":"2eTrvaDhnWCGf1MDYEkcdA","children":[]},{"id":"346","parent":"341","text":"Struma ovarii\\N(Tejido tiroideo en ovario)","guid":"KsYaBmKOLEv8qr60fRxWaw","children":[]},{"id":"347","parent":"341","text":"Metástasis funcionante de\\Ncarcinoma folicular","guid":"PFV_IVGsbkBPfD3CjWqtnA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"348","parent":"320","text":"Ecografía con\\Nmedición de flujo","guid":"_6ZlrniIyaIel3KvrSIsaQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"349","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"mLtq0R0cVbd4OHI2pELi-g","children":[{"id":"350","parent":"349","text":"Prescribir betabloqueantes para el alivio de los síntomas de la\\Ntaquicardia, los temblores y la ansiedad (Recomendación fuerte).","guid":"5rLy8z7Cq6rSSMt_JzO5hg","children":[]},{"id":"351","parent":"349","text":"El tratamiento del hipertiroidismo suele\\Ndepender de la causa subyacente.","guid":"HksyCzsWGZC5aGtXe5AQqA","children":[{"id":"352","parent":"351","text":"Trate la enfermedad de Graves con medicamentos antitiroideos,\\Nyodo radiactivo o tiroidectomía (recomendación fuerte).","guid":"JQcTeQkT8E3cVoXfvtqRnA","children":[]},{"id":"353","parent":"351","text":"Considere el tratamiento del bocio multinodular tóxico con yodo\\Nradiactivo o tiroidectomía sobre medicamentos antitiroideos","guid":"EKNfHWCe1eFmQ3fVL-qBBQ","children":[]},{"id":"354","parent":"351","text":"Considere tratar el adenoma tiroideo tóxico con yodo radiactivo\\No tiroidectomía en lugar de medicamentos antitiroideos","guid":"bHpeJ7VUL2vy7IXdreQuZQ","children":[]},{"id":"355","parent":"351","text":"Trate la tiroiditis aguda (supurativa) con antibióticos\\N(recomendación fuerte).","guid":"ctG7UFMuKlbBrXkgxzH-FQ","children":[]},{"id":"356","parent":"351","text":"Trate la tiroiditis dolorosa subaguda con cuidados de apoyo, como medicamentos\\Nantiinflamatorios no esteroideos (AINE) como terapia de primera línea o\\Ncorticosteroides si el paciente no responde a los AINE o se presenta inicialmente con\\Ndolor de moderado a intenso o síntomas de tirotoxicosis (Recomendación fuerte).","guid":"mI2YuujcWZLUKLBN4qKokw","children":[]},{"id":"357","parent":"351","text":"Tratar la tiroiditis indolora (silentada) con betabloqueantes en\\Npacientes con tirotoxicosis sintomática (recomendación fuerte).","guid":"V_y5gXm3_Zd73_265awFTA","children":[]},{"id":"358","parent":"351","text":"Tratar la tirotoxicosis tipo 1 inducida por amiodarona con methimazol (recomendación fuerte) y\\Ntratar la tirotoxicosis tipo 2 inducida por amiodarona con corticosteroides. Ocasionalmente, se\\Nrequieren tanto metimazol como corticosteroides si el tipo es incierto. (Recomendación fuerte).","guid":"ZNy2hi0KaxcSOFe6bEYdwg","children":[]},{"id":"359","parent":"351","text":"Manejar a los pacientes en una tormenta tiroidea en la unidad de cuidados intensivos\\Ncon betabloqueantes, medicamentos antitiroideos (ATD), yodo, corticosteroides,\\Nmedidas de enfriamiento agresivas y reemplazo de líquidos (recomendación fuerte).","guid":"VAnPTr4dJR3XdA7Zoy_weg","children":[]},{"id":"360","parent":"351","text":"Considere la posibilidad de tratar el hipertiroidismo subclínico en pacientes mayores\\Nde 65 años, pacientes con síntomas de hipertiroidismo y en pacientes con factores de\\Nriesgo cardíaco, enfermedad cardíaca o osteoporosis de acuerdo con los mismos\\Nprincipios utilizados en el tratamiento del hipertiroidismo manifiesto.","guid":"G5-SgspCHiubVX1lxNXXmQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"361","parent":"349","text":"Tratar el hipertiroidismo gestacional y la tirotoxicosis asociada a\\Nla hiperémesis gravidarum con terapia de apoyo, sin ATD\\N(recomendación fuerte).","guid":"0cpaL9V9WTaJ7RwASsXTOA","children":[{"id":"362","parent":"361","text":"Para las mujeres embarazadas tratadas con medicamentos antitiroideos,\\Nconsidere si se puede suspender el ATD, y si no, cambie a propil tiouracilo\\Ndurante el embarazo y durante el primer trimestre, luego, si la terapia con ATD\\Ntodavía es necesaria, cambie a methimazol en el segundo y tercer trimestre","guid":"jlROdZE7ZKNP1ruH1EzJDA","children":[]},{"id":"363","parent":"361","text":"El manejo perioperatorio en pacientes con hipertiroidismo depende\\Ndel estado clínico y de la urgencia del procedimiento.","guid":"nw_969fBsl3vjZ1vyZXMCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"364","parent":"349","text":"La cirugía (tiroidismo o no tiroideo) en aquellos con\\Nhipertiroidismo no reconocido o tratado inadecuadamente\\Npuede precipitar la tormenta tiroidea.","guid":"RSYOt_isB7VpVxP0zSx2Ag","children":[{"id":"365","parent":"364","text":"Antes de cualquier cirugía, el objetivo es lograr un estado eutiroideo.","guid":"lQGWXQncgKesAaSn4g4qkg","children":[]},{"id":"366","parent":"364","text":"Los pacientes con hipertiroidismo de moderado a grave deben esperar hasta\\Nque el hipertiroidismo esté bajo control antes de proceder a cirugías electivas.","guid":"KB983eb_etLY3rmB2xVhWA","children":[]},{"id":"367","parent":"364","text":"Si el paciente no se convierte en eutiroidea antes de la tiroidectomía, si la necesidad de cirugía es\\Nurgente, o si el paciente es alérgico a los medicamentos antitiroideos, la premedicación debe\\Nincluir betabloqueantes, yoduro de potasio, glucocorticoides y posiblemente colestiramina.","guid":"7tWbFl5kLH3xToz5kC_pOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"368","parent":"349","text":"Consideraciones ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"369","parent":"368","text":"Antitiroideos\\NInh. peroxidasa tiroidea","guid":"FjhsWefj74sjrXjurTKnEg","children":[{"id":"370","parent":"369","text":"General","guid":"oMIrHVR-N9VM8JUZRY_z9g","children":[{"id":"371","parent":"370","text":"Si hay más producción\\Nde T3-T4","guid":"bTVXUfvljDqyCyNs4s8QyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"372","parent":"369","text":"Metamizol","guid":"bee0FoOCcn-PsLQBAiE7JA","children":[]},{"id":"373","parent":"369","text":"Carbimazol","guid":"_VRp9wKmADwgOYHKvuXV9Q","children":[]},{"id":"374","parent":"369","text":"Propiltiouracilo\\NPTU","guid":"WJVeghq59QROqyS9e4amcA","children":[{"id":"375","parent":"374","text":"Inhibición\\NT4 a T3","guid":"6e75B1Y_-iWA36oah6_nSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"376","parent":"369","text":"RAM\\NAgranulocitosis\\N<500/mm3","guid":"P7lyMYXRcbwpJonxtUQQnw","children":[{"id":"377","parent":"376","text":"Evolución brusca","guid":"2s0Jk-EjAZMvT1LT1jP8hQ","children":[]},{"id":"378","parent":"376","text":"Fiebre","guid":"e6JN4-L6PGP4IG83np8Kmg","children":[]},{"id":"379","parent":"376","text":"Odinofagia","guid":"Ukv8HlVQvFFUWNkZUzdFmA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"380","parent":"368","text":"Yoduro inorganico","guid":"iTvsSz1yNU_udtEdAkRl6Q","children":[]},{"id":"381","parent":"368","text":"Glucocorticoides\\NCrisis tóxica","guid":"jOc2ZziyskLFcEbJHfNJOA","children":[{"id":"382","parent":"381","text":"Graves\\NOftalmopatía","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"383","parent":"368","text":"Yodo radioactivo","guid":"ShlDCoU8LW1xs8_n8N_M-g","children":[]},{"id":"384","parent":"368","text":"Cirugía","guid":"feVfXjpzSxoUQG_QcsgKWQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"385","parent":"0","text":"Crisis tóxica","guid":"sTVU1Wn3CUTYqfN-h-dkIQ","children":[{"id":"386","parent":"385","text":"Causa","guid":"gnMMeooFUGK-r8fqatvL-g","children":[{"id":"387","parent":"386","text":"Cirugía","guid":"F2lpE0lnwsL8Fmthd6Jv0g","children":[]},{"id":"388","parent":"386","text":"Infarto","guid":"eYSCXHQP3VFWpDNfc8lugw","children":[]},{"id":"389","parent":"386","text":"Trauma","guid":"jTEsmWpCqaRKvyF9DyG1KQ","children":[]},{"id":"390","parent":"386","text":"TEP","guid":"amptJun2CabDzf24VE3Vfw","children":[]},{"id":"391","parent":"386","text":"Infecciones","guid":"prCWWXFAo4Fy6A7rL6iB7g","children":[]},{"id":"392","parent":"386","text":"Parto","guid":"L-PWGh3kWh2I2_veMuYakg","children":[]},{"id":"393","parent":"386","text":"Cetoacidosis diabética","guid":"Di3bjf938_dCbZEhIH6bxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"394","parent":"385","text":"Clínica","guid":"718Um0GrGTWxtjtFOu4sbw","children":[{"id":"395","parent":"394","text":"Taquicardia","guid":"GKoxD9WJCqWEyZBMRkgYig","children":[]},{"id":"396","parent":"394","text":"Arritmia","guid":"9Mx5eHEnAZZhshK4hHd38w","children":[]},{"id":"397","parent":"394","text":"ICC","guid":"YRyv81Q5o5Dv1FmcrshqRg","children":[]},{"id":"398","parent":"394","text":"Hipotension","guid":"CMg_HmgaHzaz5xzJWTDvCg","children":[]},{"id":"399","parent":"394","text":"Delirium","guid":"y3FgnjyRvm9UrBNfs759Yg","children":[]},{"id":"400","parent":"394","text":"Hipertermia","guid":"Rx7_2kXKn6J4krHZolYQiw","children":[]},{"id":"401","parent":"394","text":"Falla hepatica","guid":"hs3-MoDReRm2zG5MA6ZIBw","children":[]}]},{"id":"402","parent":"385","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"gv4wSmPS6p_kfnHGzwvlYA","children":[{"id":"403","parent":"402","text":"BB","guid":"9qLJjUTXt6nu3F9Z7bvrUg","children":[]},{"id":"404","parent":"402","text":"Metamizol","guid":"k2uBN9MKSypG_hTCbqEiuw","children":[]},{"id":"405","parent":"402","text":"Yoduro in